Diamond-Star Motors Corp, thejoint-venture company owned by Chrysler Corp &lt;C> and MitsubishiMotors, named additional production suppliers for the newvehicle to be produced at the company's plant underconstruction in Bloomington, Ill.    It said Amtex Inc, Sidney, Ohio, was selected to supplytrunk floor carpets and Bluewater Plastics Inc, Marysville,Mich., duct assemblies and column covers. Reuter&#3;